    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thou, as the Life of all, from the dead art__ a-ris-en. An An-gel bright with light called out un-to the wom-en: Cease ye from tears and weep-ing; tell the A-pos-tles the tid-ings full of__ joy. Cry a-loud sing-ing prais-es, that Christ the Lord is a-ris-en from the__ dead, He that in truth hath been well-pleased, as God, to save the race of man-kind."
    }
